00:13:43.750 --> 00:13:46.050
Page 47.

00:13:52.630 --> 00:13:56.260
&gt;&gt; Dawn Lundy Martin: Always the
I is fissure recklessly yearning

00:13:56.260 --> 00:14:01.310
for its whole sense of
wholeness like a potato.

00:14:01.310 --> 00:14:07.180 position:56%
We walk backward into a room because
we want to restate our thoughts.

00:14:07.180 --> 00:14:11.830
All the brown skins are glowing
in this light and no one is afraid

00:14:11.830 --> 00:14:18.020
where all joyous but it's difficult
to tell if the joy is real joy

00:14:18.020 --> 00:14:20.890
or if it's just lack of fear.

00:14:20.890 --> 00:14:25.260
What kind of understanding
will sink into the body?

00:14:25.260 --> 00:14:29.430
It's just one body despite
other previously stated facts

00:14:29.430 --> 00:14:32.830
